116 * Ego/Vanity ‘Xp? Egolessness is impersonality. Person-ality seems to
be something, andimpersonality nothing. But that’sbecause we do not easily
see thatpersonality is limitation to a body,while impersonality is the
absence oflimitation. ...Impersonality is Con-sciousness undiminished.
